#MaskSeries : Bedawang Nala

Bedawang Nala is a giant turtle in Balinese mythology who carries the whole world on his back. In the world's creation mythology, he is a change from Antaboga. He and two dragons support the human world. If it moves, there will be earthquakes and volcanic eruptions on the earth.
